@EU_Commission So who caused that energy crisis?
UFO? Reptilians?🤔 .. or maybe Genrmany dreaming about be "energy resources hub" for whole Europe?🤔

Please tell us as on prev position you have been part of the Germany Goverment ..

@EU_Commission What sources? There are no long term substitutes! 

The EU economic area will have HIGHEST energy inputs and HUGE competitive disadvantage.

Stop this nonsense and start diplomacy and negotiations with RF.

@EU_Commission WHAT THE HECK you think a few panels mounted on rooftops are going to do in apartment buildings of 3+ floors, possibly with trees around and/or exposed to the north?

Just let's throw panels in the streets then.

What a bunch of mindless drones.

@EU_Commission It does barely make sense...
Just include nuclear energy in the taxonomy. 

Everything else is cosmetic.

@EU_Commission Apart from bunging weapons to Ukraine I see no plan to end this invasion ! 
Russia claiming they are looking at the long game ? 
No one will invest or build anything while the invasion continues ! Yet Ukraine need to get normality and the economy up and running ! No plan ?

@EU_Commission @JavierBlas @vonderleyen Please increase the push on #oil and gas #divestment. I mean really push hard. Drive that “price signal” way up there.
I don’t want to see pipelines or production growth.
Just higher and higher prices due to this idiotic supply constraint #energytransition strategy.
